{"tid":457897,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"祝賀國歌法！👍🏻快啲入黎認識下我地國家既國歌啦👍🏻👍🏻👍🏻","createTime":"2017-11-04T10:27:18.000Z","updateTime":"2017-11-04T13:59:58.000Z","uid":9581,"like":5,"dislike":46,"uniUserReply":19,"replies":[{"pid":"a667c21737aefdbdedb3ede54c379776cd6fb70f","tid":457897,"uid":9581,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-04T10:27:18.000Z","msg":"2004年3月14日第十屆全國人民代表大會第二次會議正式將《義勇軍進行曲》作為國歌寫入憲法修正案。（第四章第一百三十六條第二款：「中華人民共和國國歌是《義勇軍進行曲》。」）<br />\n<br />\n義勇軍進行曲是中華人民共和國國歌，1949年建國後，歌曲使用至今。<br />\n<br />\n原是電影《風雲兒女》的插歌，1935年由田漢作詞，聶耳作曲，亦是中華民國國民革命軍第200師的軍歌<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">歌詞：</span></span><br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">起來！不願做奴隸的人們！<br />\n把我們的血肉，築成我們新的長城！<br />\n中華民族到了最危險的時候，<br />\n每個人被迫着發出最後的吼聲。<br />\n起來！起來！起來！<br />\n我們萬眾一心，<br />\n冒着敵人的炮火，前進！<br />\n冒着敵人的炮火，前進！<br />\n前進！前進！進！</span>"},{"pid":"e936a11d834d6550a1aa89715b1c34425d504328","tid":457897,"uid":9581,"like":0,"dislike":4,"score":-4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-04T10:34:48.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a8be83d96bfa4d00f58326b4fefdd6ca8518adec","tid":457897,"uid":47359,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-04T10:35:45.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/11/04/183531_ea3dc39ca0b2f6b5f17abddec1f0e9a4.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F11%2F04%2F183531_ea3dc39ca0b2f6b5f17abddec1f0e9a4.png&h=bc9ce536&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"39e2e78c35ecdefa0036af9e4cff46bc39d9ef7a","tid":457897,"uid":63669,"like":16,"dislike":3,"score":13,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-04T10:36:14.000Z","msg":"God save our gracious Queen.<br />\nLong live our noble Queen<br />\nGod save the Queen<br />\nSend her victorious<br />\nHappy and glorious<br />\nLong to reign over us<br />\nGod save the Queen<br />\n<br />\nO Lord our God arise<br />\nScatter her enemies<br />\nAnd make them fall<br />\nConfound their politics<br />\nFrustrate their knavish tricks<br />\nOn Thee our hopes we fix<br />\nGod save us all<br />\n<br />\nThy choicest gifts in store<br />\nOn her be pleased to pour<br />\nLong may she reign<br />\nMay she defend our laws<br />\nAnd ever give us cause<br />\nTo sing with heart and voice<br />\nGod save the Queen<br />\n<br />\nNot in this land alone<br />\nBut be God's mercies known<br />\nFrom shore to shore<br />\nLord make the nations see<br />\nThat men should brothers be<br />\nAnd form one family<br />\nThe wide world over<br />\n<br />\nFrom every latent foe<br />\nFrom the assassins blow<br />\nGod save the Queen<br />\nO'er her thine arm extend<br />\nFor Britain's sake defend<br />\nOur mother, prince, and friend<br />\nGod save the Queen"},{"pid":"d7460ad76db2a11f5681f567bce26df067948dc2","tid":457897,"uid":72736,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-04T10:36:22.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/11/04/183600_ea3dc39ca0b2f6b5f17abddec1f0e9a4.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F11%2F04%2F183600_ea3dc39ca0b2f6b5f17abddec1f0e9a4.png&h=a584e5e9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n你需要再啟蒙下"},{"pid":"dd384b9f4dd9c44801b9c27b6ac01223b9205d54","tid":457897,"uid":20241,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-04T10:36:34.000Z","msg":"起來 我帶你環遊世界<br />\n我騎住哥斯拉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"445162f68e659a230def0edddedeb4e758a31683","tid":457897,"uid":71725,"like":0,"dislike":7,"score":-7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-04T10:37:20.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"0d4250732358fbc90b1ab2b5c58ac89cbf893812","tid":457897,"uid":72736,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-04T10:38:54.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>起來 我帶你環遊世