"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-04T12:16:03.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>God save our gracious Queen.<br />\nLong live our noble Queen<br />\nGod save the Queen<br />\nSend her victorious<br />\nHappy and glorious<br />\nLong to reign over us<br />\nGod save the Queen<br />\n<br />\nO Lord our God arise<br />\nScatter her enemies<br />\nAnd make them fall<br />\nConfound their politics<br />\nFrustrate their knavish tricks<br />\nOn Thee our hopes we fix<br />\nGod save us all<br />\n<br />\nThy choicest gifts in store<br />\nOn her be pleased to pour<br />\nLong may she reign<br />\nMay she defend our laws<br />\nAnd ever give us cause<br />\nTo sing with heart and voice<br />\nGod save the Queen<br />\n<br />\nNot in this land alone<br />\nBut be God's mercies known<br />\nFrom shore to shore<br />\nLord make the nations see<br />\nThat men should brothers be<br />\nAnd form one family<br />\nThe wide world over<br />\n<br />\nFrom every latent foe<br />\nFrom the assassins blow<br />\nGod save the Queen<br />\nO'er her thine arm extend<br />\nFor Britain's sake defend<br />\nOur mother, prince, and friend<br />\nGod save the Queen</blockquote></blockquote>"},{"pid":"a2175f916252a45ea2cded8f4c9d931991b3594b","tid":457897,"uid":9581,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-04T12:39:21.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">支持立法!</span></span><br />\n連登班垃圾不代表我們中國香港人</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e85e19c347ee810927da92787865d8b5284d591e","tid":457897,"uid":38255,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-04T13:52:51.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>作為全國知名的劇作家，與不少中共文化人一樣，難逃被打倒的命運。<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">文化大革命期間，田漢被扣上「資產階級反動學術權威」的帽子，鬥倒批臭，受盡折磨侮辱，兒子更公開宣布與他劃清界線</span></span>。田漢在囚室一樣的醫院病房中度過生命最後的歲月，死時身邊一個親人都沒有<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/41.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/33.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n聶耳4月16日從上海抵達日本，期間寄出《義勇軍進行曲》，7月17日在神奈川鵠沼海濱溺亡。<br />\n<br />\n抗日歌係日本寫<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/06.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"30612ee91d7a1cf6e23fe94b2d5ad6a62f3f39ca","tid":457897,"uid":61280,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-04T13:56:25.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/11/04/215622_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F11%2F04%2F215622_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg&h=f799d0fa&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"7fc36679067eb741928fd6defb5d9a03cbf07cfd","tid":457897,"uid":103156,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-04T13:57:03.000Z","msg":"梅花梅花滿天下<br />\n愈冷它愈開花<br />\n梅花堅忍象徵我們<br />\n巍巍的<span style=\"color: blue;\">大中華</span><br />\n<br />\n看啊遍地開了梅花<br />\n有土地就有它<br />\n冰雪風雨它都不怕<br />\n它是<span style=\"color: pink;\">我的國花</span>"}]}